title: Web Extra: Drew Lock and Gary Pinkel preview matchup with Georgia
text: Drew Locks talks about what he needs to do to improve off his bad game against Florida. Gary Pinkel talks about Will Grier's suspension, Nick Chubb's injury and his evaluation of Drew Lock.
